\
4. Open the "Cruncher Tutorial Scene" in the Cruncher/Scenes folder.\
\
5. Click on the Dinosaur game object in the hierarchy window.\
\
6. In the menu bar, you should have a sub-menu under the GameObject menu called "Cruncher". Choose "Convert Selection\'85" in the menu.\
\
