\
8. Click on the game object, now called "Dinosaur LOD 0".\
\
9. In the inspector you can now see the Cruncher settings. Click "Live Preview" and then try dragging the Quality slider. You'll notice the mesh will automatically adapt and update.\
\
10. Once you have finished adjusting the game object, click "Accept" to update the mesh on disk and save it. Click "Revert" to undo the changes you made.\
